WEBVTT

00:00.534 --> 00:02.318
<i> PREVIOUSLY</i>
<i> ON "SECRETS & LIES"...</i>

00:02.319 --> 00:04.103
JESS IS BIPOLAR
AND GOES OFF HER MEDS.

00:04.105 --> 00:05.555
HOW VIOLENT DOES SHE GET?

00:05.556 --> 00:07.006
THERE'S NO WAY
THAT SHE KILLED TOM.

00:07.008 --> 00:08.691
THE FIRST BLOW
HAPPENED HERE,

00:08.692 --> 00:10.375
AND THEN SHE CHASED HIM
BACK THERE, WHERE HE DIED.

00:10.378 --> 00:12.044
I THOUGHT YOU WERE
LOOKING AT BEN CRAWFORD.

00:12.046 --> 00:13.546
TOM'S KILLER IS FEMALE.

00:13.547 --> 00:15.047
YOU DON'T KNOW WHAT IT'S LIKE
TO LOSE A CHILD!

00:15.049 --> 00:16.515
I LOVED TOM, TOO!

00:17.451 --> 00:19.351
YOU STILL HAVE YOURS!

00:19.353 --> 00:20.352
Christy:
Is Abby with you?

00:20.354 --> 00:21.387
WHAT?

00:21.388 --> 00:22.421
I'VE LOOKED EVERYWHERE,
BEN.

00:22.423 --> 00:23.422
She's gone.

00:23.424 --> 00:25.024
DO YOU HAVE ABBY
IN THERE?!

00:25.026 --> 00:26.091
YOU LOST
YOUR DAUGHTER NOW?

00:26.093 --> 00:26.759
FEELS HORRIBLE,
DOESN'T IT?

00:26.761 --> 00:28.260
I'LL KILL YOU!

00:31.499 --> 00:33.732
Ben: ABBY!

00:33.734 --> 00:35.167
ABBY!

00:35.169 --> 00:36.435
ABBY!

00:36.437 --> 00:39.171
OPEN THE DAMN DOOR,
JESS!

00:50.818 --> 00:55.054
[ CELLPHONE RINGING ]

00:55.056 --> 00:56.688
HEY.
BEN,
WHERE IS SHE?

00:56.690 --> 00:59.291
WE'RE GONNA FIND HER.
I'm scared.

00:59.293 --> 01:01.560
I KNOW. I AM, TOO.
BUT YOU GOT TO STAY CALM.

01:01.562 --> 01:02.828
GOD, WHAT IF --
DON'T EVEN SAY IT.

01:02.830 --> 01:04.113
It's been hours.
[ BEEP ]

01:04.114 --> 01:05.397
ALL RIGHT.
THAT'S THE OTHER LINE.

01:05.399 --> 01:06.231
IT COULD BE NEWS.

01:06.233 --> 01:08.233
CALL ME BACK.
I will.

01:08.235 --> 01:10.369
BEN CRAWFORD.
MR. CRAWFORD.

01:10.371 --> 01:12.704
DID ELAINE CALL YOU?
YES, SHE DID.

01:12.706 --> 01:14.740
JESS HAS ABBY. I DON'T KNOW
WHAT SHE'S CAPABLE OF.

01:14.742 --> 01:17.109
OFFICERS ARE ON THEIR WAY
TO YOU RIGHT NOW.

01:17.111 --> 01:18.844
[ SIRENS WAILING ]

01:18.846 --> 01:22.114
ALL RIGHT. I SEE THEM.
THEY'RE HERE.
Mr. Crawford,

01:22.116 --> 01:24.416
DID YOU RAPE
JESS MURPHY?

01:33.127 --> 01:34.760
MR. CRAWFORD,
ARE YOU THERE?

01:34.762 --> 01:36.528
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

01:36.530 --> 01:37.830
MR. CRAWFORD?
YEAH, I'M HERE.

01:37.832 --> 01:39.498
UH -- BE RIGHT THERE!

01:39.500 --> 01:41.567
UH, CAN YOU HOLD ON?
I GOT TO LET THE COPS IN.

01:41.569 --> 01:42.734
OF COURSE.

01:42.736 --> 01:44.103
[ CELLPHONE BEEPS ]

01:44.105 --> 01:45.437
MR. CRAWFORD?

01:45.439 --> 01:46.572
[ CELLPHONE BEEPS ]

01:46.574 --> 01:47.739
SON OF A BITCH.

01:47.741 --> 01:49.842
[ DOOR SLAMS ]

01:49.844 --> 01:52.111
[ POLICE RADIO CHATTER ]

02:09.130 --> 02:10.195
WHERE'S ABBY?!
GET OUT OF MY HOUSE!

02:10.197 --> 02:12.231
ABBY!
GET OUT OF MY HOUSE!

02:12.233 --> 02:13.265
GET OUT OF MY HOUSE!
Man: POLICE! OPEN UP!

02:13.267 --> 02:15.167
WHAT DID YOU DO TO HER?

02:15.169 --> 02:17.202
WHAT DID YOU DO
WITH MY DAUGHTER?!
I DON'T HAVE HER!

02:17.204 --> 02:18.337
WHERE IS SHE?
GET YOUR HANDS UP!

02:18.339 --> 02:19.338
WHERE THE HELL IS SHE?
AAH!

02:19.340 --> 02:21.140
HANDS UP!
SHE HAS MY DAUGHTER!

02:21.142 --> 02:21.773
MR. CRAWFORD, PLEASE.

02:21.775 --> 02:23.142
DOWN ON THE GROUND.

02:23.144 --> 02:25.177
GET YOUR HANDS UP<i> NOW.</i>

02:29.583 --> 02:30.916
LAST NIGHT, HE RAPED ME!
Woman:
IT'S GONNA BE OKAY.

02:30.918 --> 02:32.268
THAT'S A LIE!

02:32.269 --> 02:33.619
THAT'S WHY HE BROKE INTO
MY HOUSE TODAY.
I UNDERSTAND.

02:33.621 --> 02:34.637
YOU'RE A LIAR!

02:34.638 --> 02:35.654
I'M SCARED.
IT'LL BE ALL RIGHT.

02:35.656 --> 02:36.922
MR. CRAWFORD.
SHE HAS MY DAUGHTER.

02:36.924 --> 02:38.257
YOU'VE GOT
TO HELP ME FIND HER!
LET'S GO.

02:38.258 --> 02:39.591
WHY WON'T YOU --
YOU'VE GOT TO LISTEN TO ME!

02:39.593 --> 02:40.743
PLEASE!
I DON'T KNOW.

02:40.744 --> 02:41.894
HE JUST RAN IN.
Officer: IT'S ALL RIGHT.

02:41.896 --> 02:43.829
BROKE THE WINDOW.
RIGHT THIS WAY.

02:52.473 --> 02:53.656
Jess: I DIDN'T
DO ANYTHING WRONG.

02:53.657 --> 02:54.840
Man:
ALL RIGHT, LET'S GO.
HE'S CRAZY.

02:54.842 --> 02:57.509
SHE'S GOT
MY DAUGHTER!

02:57.511 --> 03:00.279
SHE HAS ABBY!
THE WOMAN IS DERANGED!

03:00.281 --> 03:01.346
[ CAR DOOR OPENS ]

03:04.218 --> 03:06.618
[ ENGINE TURNS OVER ]

03:06.620 --> 03:08.754
GET IN.
[ POLICE RADIO CHATTER ]

03:08.756 --> 03:10.222
NOTIFY THE PRECINCT.
[ SIREN CHIRPS ]

03:10.224 --> 03:11.823
Officer: DETECTIVE.

03:11.825 --> 03:14.326
YOU NEED TO SEE THIS.

03:20.935 --> 03:22.701
BLUE JACKET.

03:32.246 --> 03:34.313
[ SIREN WAILING ]

03:38.886 --> 03:40.352
JESS HAS DONE SOMETHING
WITH ABBY.

03:40.354 --> 03:41.887
I'M TELLING YOU.
YOU GOT TO HELP ME.

03:41.889 --> 03:43.789
YOUR DAUGHTER'S FINE,
MR. CRAWFORD.

03:43.791 --> 03:44.957
WHAT?
SHE'S AT
YOUR BROTHER-IN-LAW'S.

03:44.959 --> 03:46.392
SHE'S WITH HER MOTHER.

03:46.393 --> 03:47.826
SHE WENT FOR A WALK
AND DIDN'T TELL ANYBODY.

03:47.828 --> 03:49.895
[ EXHALES DEEPLY ]
SHE'S SAFE AND SOUND.

03:49.897 --> 03:51.797
[ SIGHS ]

03:51.799 --> 03:53.349
I WANT TO TALK TO HER.

03:53.350 --> 03:54.900
AS SOON AS WE'RE DONE HERE,
YOU CAN.

03:54.902 --> 03:56.902
OKAY,
I DON'T CARE WHAT SHE SAID.

03:56.904 --> 03:58.604
I DIDN'T RAPE JESS MURPHY.

03:58.606 --> 03:59.738
SO YOU'VE SAID.

03:59.740 --> 04:01.323
I SLEPT WITH HER,

04:01.324 --> 04:02.907
BUT I WENT TO BED WITH
ONE WOMAN AND WOKE UP
WITH ANOTHER ONE.

04:02.910 --> 04:04.677
SHE IS CRAZY.

04:04.678 --> 04:06.445
I'M AWARE OF
JESS MURPHY'S MEDICAL HISTORY.

04:06.447 --> 04:08.614
DID YOU KNOW THAT SHE HAD
ANOTHER CHILD WHO DIED?

04:08.616 --> 04:09.648
AND THEN THERE'S TOM?

04:13.854 --> 04:15.754
WHERE'D
YOU FIND THAT?

04:15.756 --> 04:19.458
I FOUND THAT SOAKING
IN JESS MURPHY'S LAUNDRY SINK.

04:19.460 --> 04:21.727
COME ON.
THIS IS INSANE.

04:21.729 --> 04:23.129
I DIDN'T RAPE JESS,

04:23.130 --> 04:24.530
I DIDN'T
PUT THAT IN HER SINK,

04:24.531 --> 04:25.931
AND I HAVEN'T SEEN
THAT JACKET SINCE
THE DAY IN THE WOODS.

04:25.933 --> 04:28.600
I KNOW, MR. CRAWFORD.

04:30.037 --> 04:31.770
WHAT DO YOU KNOW?

04:31.772 --> 04:34.273
I KNOW ALL ABOUT
JESS MURPHY.

04:34.275 --> 04:37.442
I KNOW
YOU DIDN'T HAVE THE JACKET.

04:38.812 --> 04:40.879
AND I KNOW
YOU DIDN'T KILL TOM.

04:44.885 --> 04:46.285
YOU KNOW?

04:46.887 --> 04:48.387
I DO.

04:49.790 --> 04:51.857
YOU'RE FREE TO GO.

04:57.798 --> 04:59.298
GO HOME, MR. CRAWFORD.

05:01.902 --> 05:03.702
OKAY.

05:06.073 --> 05:08.807
[ DOOR OPENS, CLOSES ]

05:13.514 --> 05:14.880
ABBY: I'm sorry, Dad.
I wanted to be by myself.

05:14.882 --> 05:16.165
I'M JUST GLAD
YOU'RE OKAY.

05:16.166 --> 05:17.449
YOU AND MOM
HATE EACH OTHER, AND --

05:17.451 --> 05:18.517
I DON'T
HATE YOUR FATHER.

05:18.519 --> 05:19.851
I DON'T
HATE YOUR MOTHER.

05:19.853 --> 05:21.586
And Nat acts
like nothing happened.

05:21.588 --> 05:23.655
I GOT SAD.

05:23.657 --> 05:25.557
BUT I DIDN'T MEAN
TO SCARE YOU.

05:25.559 --> 05:28.694
Mom's really mad,
though.
YEAH, SO AM I.

05:28.696 --> 05:30.729
WE HAVE TO KNOW
WHERE YOU ARE, ABBY.

05:30.731 --> 05:33.565
YOU CAN'T JUST LEAVE
AND NOT TELL ANYONE.
I know.

05:33.567 --> 05:35.767
DO YOU FORGIVE ME?

05:35.769 --> 05:37.703
IF YOU PROMISE
TO NEVER DO IT AGAIN.

05:37.705 --> 05:40.372
I PROMISE.
ABBY.

05:41.942 --> 05:44.009
MOM WANTS
TO TALK TO YOU.

05:45.946 --> 05:47.379
IT'S ME.

05:47.381 --> 05:49.181
YOU OKAY?

05:49.182 --> 05:50.982
I THINK THE NIGHTMARE'S
FINALLY OVER.

05:50.984 --> 05:52.918
What do you mean?
What happened?

05:52.920 --> 05:55.887
THE BLUE JACKET
WAS JESS'.

05:56.690 --> 05:58.490
JESS KILLED TOM?

05:58.492 --> 06:01.426
IT LOOKS LIKE IT.
I can't believe this.

06:03.964 --> 06:05.897
COPS ARE BRINGING HER IN.
I GOT TO GO.

06:17.878 --> 06:21.513
[ TWEEDY'S "THE WOLF
IS ON THE HILL" PLAYS ]

06:25.986 --> 06:29.087
¶ THE WOLF IS ON THE HILL ¶

06:29.089 --> 06:31.757
¶ THE BIRD IS IN THE BRIAR ¶

06:31.759 --> 06:32.958
DID YOU DRUG THIS?

06:32.960 --> 06:34.960
OH, COME ON.
I LEARNED MY LESSON...

06:34.962 --> 06:36.628
LIGHTWEIGHT.
¶ THE THORN
IS ON THE ROSE ¶

06:36.630 --> 06:38.764
YEAH. THAT'S MY BOY.
[ LAUGHS ]

06:38.766 --> 06:40.799
¶ AND YOUR TIME
IS ON THE WIRE ¶

06:40.801 --> 06:42.317
AHH.

06:42.318 --> 06:43.834
SO, WHAT DO YOU WANT TO DO
FOR DINNER?

06:43.837 --> 06:45.621
I CAN'T STAY.
I GOT A DATE.

06:45.622 --> 06:47.406
¶ THOSE DAYS
OF GRAVE CONCERN ¶

06:47.408 --> 06:48.907
WHAT TIME
DOES SHE LOG ON?

06:48.909 --> 06:51.576
SHE'S ACTUALLY
A REAL PERSON.

06:51.578 --> 06:53.845
SHE'S 5'2"...

06:53.847 --> 06:55.080
BRAINS, BEAUTY,
GOT IT ALL.

06:55.082 --> 06:56.782
SHE'S A KINDERGARTEN
TEACHER.

06:56.784 --> 06:58.750
SHE LOVES KIDS.

06:58.752 --> 06:59.885
SHE LOVES HORROR MOVIES.

06:59.887 --> 07:02.120
SHE LOVES ALL THIS.

07:02.122 --> 07:03.889
AS WELL SHE SHOULD.

07:03.891 --> 07:05.991
AND SHE SAYS I MAKE
HER LAUGH FOR SOME REASON,

07:05.993 --> 07:07.192
WHICH IS WEIRD.
I CAN SEE THAT.

07:07.194 --> 07:08.560
I MET HER
AT A GAS STATION.

07:08.562 --> 07:10.495
SHE, UH, NEEDED SOME AIR
IN HER TIRES.

07:10.497 --> 07:12.030
AND YOU FIGURED OUT
HOW TO DO IT?

07:12.032 --> 07:14.099
NO. I GOT SOME OTHER DUDE
TO HANDLE IT,

07:14.101 --> 07:15.500
AND THEN I MADE MY MOVE.

07:15.502 --> 07:17.502
SLICK.
MM.

07:17.504 --> 07:19.871
I THINK IT'S THE
FIRST TIME I HAD A
DATE FOR NEW YEAR'S.

07:19.873 --> 07:22.007
¶ THE ROAD
HAS TURNED TO SAND ¶

07:22.009 --> 07:24.709
YEAH.
¶ THAT YOUR WILL
HAS SUNKEN INTO ¶

07:24.711 --> 07:25.577
I'M SORRY.

07:25.579 --> 07:27.446
NO, DON'T. COME ON.

07:27.448 --> 07:29.164
YOU KNOW WHAT?

07:29.165 --> 07:30.881
YOU CAN ROCK IN THE HOLIDAYS
WITH YOUR KIDS, RIGHT?

07:30.884 --> 07:33.985
BECAUSE CHRISTY HAS TO LOOSEN UP
FOR A FREE MAN.

07:33.987 --> 07:35.787
RIGHT?

07:35.789 --> 07:38.757
[ SIGHS ] FREE MAN.

07:38.759 --> 07:39.991
TO FREEDOM.

07:39.993 --> 07:41.693
TO FREEDOM!

07:41.695 --> 07:44.629
HELLS TO THE YES,
BROTHER.

07:44.631 --> 07:47.232
FREEDOM!!

07:47.234 --> 07:48.500
[ LAUGHS ]

07:52.840 --> 07:55.140
Jess: HE BROKE INTO THE HOUSE,
AND HE ASSAULTED ME.

07:55.142 --> 07:57.909
DID MR. CRAWFORD
HIT YOU?
NO! HE GRABBED ME.

07:57.911 --> 08:01.246
HE -- HE PUT HIS HANDS ON ME
AND HE SHOOK ME.

08:01.248 --> 08:04.249
DID YOU SEE
ABBY CRAWFORD TODAY?
NO.
I NEVER HAD ABBY.

08:04.251 --> 08:07.586
NO MATTER WHAT BEN SAYS,
I DIDN'T<i> DO</i> ANYTHING WRONG.

08:07.588 --> 08:10.155
I'M NOT BLAMING YOU,
MRS. MURPHY.

08:10.157 --> 08:11.523
IF YOU'D LIKE TO FILE

08:11.525 --> 08:13.158
A COMPLAINT
AGAINST MR. CRAWFORD,

08:13.160 --> 08:14.659
I'LL TAKE YOUR STATEMENT

08:14.661 --> 08:16.061
AND THEN WE'LL GO DOWN
TO THE HOSPITAL,

08:16.063 --> 08:18.413
WHERE THEY'LL EXAMINE YOU

08:18.414 --> 08:20.764
AND WILL DOCUMENT YOUR INJURIES
AND GET A RAPE KIT.

08:21.969 --> 08:23.235
OKAY?

08:25.839 --> 08:27.105
NOW HAVE A SEAT.

08:33.580 --> 08:34.513
[ SIGHS ]

08:36.149 --> 08:39.050
CAN YOU TELL ME
EXACTLY WHAT HAPPENED?

08:40.988 --> 08:43.655
WE WENT TO GO SEE
THE FIREWORKS.

08:43.657 --> 08:44.856
BEN DROVE ME HOME.

08:44.858 --> 08:47.926
HE WAS LONELY.

08:47.928 --> 08:50.295
AND HE INVITED HIMSELF
INTO MY HOUSE.

08:50.297 --> 08:51.897
AND THEN
WHAT HAPPENED?

08:51.899 --> 08:53.298
AND THEN HE RAPED ME.

08:53.300 --> 08:54.933
HE RAN AWAY
IN THE MORNING,

08:54.935 --> 08:56.701
BUT HE BROKE INTO
MY HOUSE

08:56.703 --> 08:58.837
AND ACCUSED ME
OF KILLING MY OWN SON.

09:01.008 --> 09:02.424
SO, HE RAPED YOU,

09:02.425 --> 09:03.841
AND THEN HE SPENT
THE ENTIRE NIGHT

09:03.844 --> 09:05.143
SLEEPING NEXT TO YOU?

09:07.648 --> 09:10.081
YOU REALIZE THAT BY FALSIFYING
A POLICE REPORT,

09:10.083 --> 09:11.816
YOU MAKE IT
INCREDIBLY DIFFICULT

09:11.818 --> 09:13.118
FOR ANY WOMAN
WHO<i> HAS</i> BEEN RAPED

09:13.120 --> 09:14.853
TO COME FORWARD.

09:14.855 --> 09:16.922
SO, IF YOU WANT
TO PURSUE THIS

09:16.924 --> 09:18.857
AND I FIND OUT
THAT YOU'VE LIED,

09:18.859 --> 09:20.292
I'LL NOT ONLY CHARGE YOU,

09:20.293 --> 09:21.726
BUT I'LL MAKE SURE
THAT YOU SERVE

09:21.728 --> 09:23.261
EVERY SINGLE DAY
OF THAT SENTENCE.

09:23.263 --> 09:24.763
IS THAT CLEAR?

09:27.701 --> 09:29.167
[ SIGHS ]

09:34.007 --> 09:36.641
[ CHUCKLES ]

09:36.643 --> 09:38.777
WHY IS THIS
HAPPENING TO ME?

09:38.779 --> 09:40.278
I DON'T KNOW
THE ANSWER TO THAT.

09:40.280 --> 09:42.681
BUT YOU'VE BEEN
LOCKED DOWN ONCE BEFORE

09:42.683 --> 09:44.416
ON A 72-HOUR HOLD.

09:44.417 --> 09:46.150
I'M SURE YOU DON'T
WANT TO BE INSTITUTIONALIZED

09:46.153 --> 09:47.152
LIKE YOUR MOTHER.

09:47.154 --> 09:48.787
I'M NOT LIKE HER!

09:53.193 --> 09:54.859
THAT'S MY JACKET.

09:56.363 --> 09:57.996
IS THAT BLOOD?

09:57.998 --> 10:00.865
YOUR SON'S KILLER
WAS WEARING YOUR JACKET.

10:07.240 --> 10:09.007
[ SNIFFLES, WHIMPERS ]

10:09.009 --> 10:10.909
I DIDN'T KILL TOM.

10:10.911 --> 10:13.945
I DIDN'T KILL TOM.
I DIDN'T KILL MY SON.

10:13.947 --> 10:16.748
I KNOW YOU DIDN'T,
MRS. MURPHY.

10:18.385 --> 10:20.919
SOMEONE IS TRYING
TO FRAME YOU.

10:37.070 --> 10:38.637
DAD?

10:38.639 --> 10:41.006
DAD!
HE'S OUT HERE.

10:41.742 --> 10:42.874
HEY.

10:42.876 --> 10:43.842
[ CHUCKLES ]

10:43.844 --> 10:45.977
HEY.

10:45.979 --> 10:48.847
I MISSED YOU.

10:48.849 --> 10:49.948
ME TOO.

10:49.950 --> 10:51.883
THAT'S NICE TO HEAR.

10:51.885 --> 10:54.152
BUT DON'T TELL ANYONE
I SAID THAT.
ALL RIGHT.

10:54.154 --> 10:56.388
WHAT'S ALL THIS?

10:56.390 --> 10:57.822
THE GIRLS BEGGED.

10:57.824 --> 11:00.859
YOU GUYS NEVER GOT
THE CHRISTMAS YOU WANTED.

11:00.861 --> 11:01.926
I HOPE
NEW YEAR'S IS OKAY.

11:01.928 --> 11:04.262
DEFINITELY.

11:04.264 --> 11:06.798
COME ON.

11:07.434 --> 11:08.833
THANK YOU.

11:17.344 --> 11:18.977
Cornell: THANK YOU ALL
FOR COMING IN.

11:18.979 --> 11:21.446
THIS SHOULD ONLY TAKE
A MINUTE.

11:21.448 --> 11:23.148
HAVE ANY OF YOU
SEEN HER?

11:35.929 --> 11:37.862
HMM. I DID.

11:37.864 --> 11:39.230
YESTERDAY.

11:39.232 --> 11:41.266
DROPPED HER OFF
NEAR CHELSEA BAY DRIVE.

11:41.268 --> 11:43.868
WHAT TIME?
LIKE, 4:00 OR 5:00.

11:43.870 --> 11:45.470
IT WAS NEAR
THE END OF MY SHIFT.

11:45.472 --> 11:48.306
WAS SHE WITH ANYBODY?
NOT THAT I SAW.

11:48.308 --> 11:51.176
I'M GONNA NEED TO REVIEW
YOUR SECURITY FOOTAGE.

11:52.946 --> 11:54.212
THANK YOU.

11:56.383 --> 11:58.116
HEY, COME HERE.

12:02.322 --> 12:04.322
I DON'T WANT TO MAKE THIS
ANY HARDER FOR THE GIRLS

12:04.324 --> 12:06.958
THAN IT ALREADY IS, BUT...

12:06.960 --> 12:09.427
IT'S SIGNED.
[ SIGHS ]

12:09.429 --> 12:11.296
HARD TO BELIEVE
17 YEARS OF MARRIAGE

12:11.298 --> 12:12.964
IS GONE
IN THE STROKE OF A PEN.

12:12.966 --> 12:15.734
IT'S NOT GONE.

12:15.736 --> 12:18.970
WE DID TWO THINGS RIGHT.

12:18.972 --> 12:21.806
THANKS FOR
BRINGING THEM OVER.
MM.

12:24.111 --> 12:26.377
I CAN'T BELIEVE
JESS KILLED TOM.
[ SCOFFS ]

12:26.379 --> 12:29.247
I REALLY DON'T WANT TO
TALK ABOUT THIS ANYMORE.
ME EITHER.

12:29.249 --> 12:30.749
WELL,
I THINK WE SHOULD.

12:30.751 --> 12:32.884
I DON'T WANT ANY MORE SECRETS
IN THIS FAMILY.

12:32.886 --> 12:33.952
THEY'RE POISON.

12:33.954 --> 12:34.953
I JUST DON'T GET IT.

12:34.955 --> 12:37.522
I MEAN,
WHY WOULD SHE DO IT?

12:37.524 --> 12:39.924
SHE HAD MORE PROBLEMS
THAN WE KNEW.

12:39.926 --> 12:42.494
MORE THAN YOU KNEW.
TOO SOON?

12:42.496 --> 12:44.329
WHY ARE WE
TALKING ABOUT JESS?

12:44.331 --> 12:46.898
DAD, DO YOU REALLY THINK
SHE DID IT?

12:46.900 --> 12:49.434
I DON'T WANT TO,
BUT, YEAH, I DO.

12:49.436 --> 12:51.136
CAN WE EAT?

12:51.137 --> 12:52.837
[ Chuckling ]
YES, WE CAN EAT.

12:52.839 --> 12:53.905
GIVE ME TWO MINUTES,
OKAY?

12:53.907 --> 12:54.939
I GOT TO CLEAN UP
SOME STUFF.

12:57.911 --> 12:58.943
N-- WHAT DO YOU MEAN,
NO?

12:58.945 --> 13:00.456
I THINK
I WAS PRETTY CLEAR.

13:00.457 --> 13:01.968
KEN, WE NEED
TO CHARGE HER.
WE CAN'T.

13:01.969 --> 13:03.480
YOU CAME TO ME WITH
A LOT MORE EVIDENCE
ON BEN CRAWFORD.

13:03.483 --> 13:04.949
I DIDN'T CHARGE HIM.
YOU DON'T HAVE IT.

13:04.951 --> 13:06.084
SHE KILLED TOM MURPHY.

13:06.086 --> 13:07.852
IF YOU CAN'T
PROVE IT TO ME,

13:07.854 --> 13:09.187
I CAN'T PROVE IT
TO A JURY.

13:09.189 --> 13:10.922
YOU'RE LAZY.
HANG ON A SECOND.

13:10.924 --> 13:13.291
I GOT 23 CASES ON MY DESK.
I JUST LOST TWO IN A ROW.

13:13.293 --> 13:15.193
NOW, UNLESS YOU CAN GIVE ME
A SLAM DUNK,

13:15.195 --> 13:17.028
WE CAN'T AFFORD
TO TAKE THIS TO TRIAL.

13:17.030 --> 13:19.964
WHAT DO YOU WANT FROM ME?
A MURDER WEAPON, A CONFESSION.

13:19.966 --> 13:22.267
BOTH WOULD BE GREAT.

13:22.269 --> 13:24.135
[ ELEVATOR BELL DINGS ]

13:56.536 --> 14:00.071
Christy:
DO YOU WANT SOME RICE?
OH, YES, PLEASE.

14:00.073 --> 14:01.906
WHAT ABOUT YOU, ABBY?
WOULD YOU LIKE SOME?

14:01.908 --> 14:03.274
Abby: NO, THANKS.
SMELLS REALLY GOOD.

14:03.276 --> 14:05.076
NO, I THINK I'M GOOD.

14:09.950 --> 14:12.584
ABBY, IS THIS BLOOD
ON YOUR SNEAKERS?

14:18.992 --> 14:21.226
IS THIS BLOOD?

14:25.999 --> 14:28.533
I'M SO SORRY, DADDY.

14:31.137 --> 14:32.971
DID YOU FIND TOM?

14:36.076 --> 14:37.008
[ Nervously ] NO.

14:39.512 --> 14:41.212
TELL ME THE TRUTH.

14:43.383 --> 14:45.450
I DIDN'T WANT
TO GET IN TROUBLE.

14:49.055 --> 14:52.523
YOU DIDN'T WANT
TO GET IN TROUBLE FOR WHAT?

15:01.201 --> 15:04.135
ABBY, WERE YOU
WITH TOM BEFORE...?

15:06.606 --> 15:07.538
YES.

15:07.540 --> 15:08.539
[ SIGHS ]
Christy: NO.

15:10.543 --> 15:12.543
NO. PLEASE, NO.

15:18.184 --> 15:19.484
[ BREATHES SHALLOWLY ]

15:23.957 --> 15:25.924
ABBY, DID YOU HURT TOM?

15:27.093 --> 15:30.128
[ Crying ] I DIDN'T MEAN TO!
IT WAS AN ACCIDENT!

15:32.032 --> 15:33.398
WHAT DID YOU DO?

15:34.935 --> 15:36.000
[ SNIFFLES ]

15:36.603 --> 15:39.103
WE WERE RUNNING AWAY.

15:41.074 --> 15:44.075
SCOTT AND JESS WERE FIGHTING,
AND SO WERE YOU.

15:44.077 --> 15:46.044
IT MADE US SO SAD.

15:46.046 --> 15:49.580
I THOUGHT I HAD
A WAY TO FIX IT.

15:55.722 --> 15:57.555
[ KEYS JINGLE ]

16:51.211 --> 16:54.045
Tom, get up.

16:54.047 --> 16:57.048
Tom, Tom. Get up.

16:57.050 --> 16:59.017
Hi.
Hi.

16:59.019 --> 17:01.085
IS IT TIME
TO WAKE UP?

17:01.087 --> 17:02.487
No.
It's still night.

17:02.489 --> 17:05.323
But we're running away,
so we have to go now.

17:05.325 --> 17:07.792
WHY?
WHEN YOUR MOMMY FINDS OUT
YOU'RE GONE,

17:07.794 --> 17:10.061
YOUR DADDY
WILL COME BACK.

17:10.063 --> 17:11.562
REALLY?

17:11.564 --> 17:14.032
THEY ALWAYS COME BACK
WHEN WE'RE IN TROUBLE.

17:15.435 --> 17:17.635
YAY!
Shh!

17:17.637 --> 17:18.770
SORRY.

17:22.342 --> 17:23.674
OH, CAN I BRING MY TANK?

17:24.811 --> 17:27.078
Okay.
Just be really quiet.

17:55.141 --> 17:56.574
Shh.

18:28.775 --> 18:30.842
[ THUNDER CRASHES ]

18:42.889 --> 18:45.523
Tom:
ABBY, I'M SCARED.

18:45.525 --> 18:47.391
IT'S OKAY, SILLY.
I'M HERE.

18:47.393 --> 18:49.660
I WON'T LET ANYTHING
HAPPEN TO YOU.

18:49.662 --> 18:52.130
THERE'S A SPECIAL SPOT
NEAR THE RIVER.

18:52.132 --> 18:55.133
WE'LL HIDE THERE
UNTIL YOUR DADDY FINDS US.

18:57.871 --> 18:58.769
MY TANK!
WHAT?

18:58.771 --> 19:00.671
I LOST MY TANK!

19:00.673 --> 19:02.240
WE'LL FIND IT.

19:02.242 --> 19:04.475
IT'S GOT TO BE HERE
SOMEWHERE.

19:05.345 --> 19:07.712
I NEED IT. IT'S GONE!

19:07.714 --> 19:09.514
DON'T WORRY.
WE'LL GET ANOTHER ONE.

19:09.516 --> 19:12.517
I DON'T WANT ANOTHER ONE.
I WANT MINE.
WE HAVE TO HURRY.

19:12.519 --> 19:14.652
NO, I'M COLD
AND I WANT TO GO HOME.

19:14.654 --> 19:16.187
NO, TOM,
IF YOU GO HOME NOW,

19:16.189 --> 19:18.189
YOUR DADDY
WILL NEVER COME BACK.
NO!

19:18.191 --> 19:19.557
I'M TELLING ON YOU!

19:19.559 --> 19:20.892
I'M GOING HOME NOW!

19:22.362 --> 19:23.828
TOM, WAIT! STOP!

19:23.830 --> 19:25.897
I WANT MY MOMMY!

19:25.899 --> 19:27.165
I WANT MY MOMMY!

19:27.167 --> 19:28.199
[ GRUNTS ]

19:34.874 --> 19:36.207
[ GASPS ]

19:38.778 --> 19:40.711
[ Crying ] I'M SORRY.

19:40.713 --> 19:44.415
COME ON. WE HAVE TO GO.
PLEASE GET UP.

19:44.417 --> 19:45.483
COME ON, TOM.

19:45.485 --> 19:47.552
PLEASE GET UP.

19:47.554 --> 19:49.787
[ BREATHING SHALLOWLY ]

19:49.789 --> 19:51.689
[ GRUNTS ]

19:53.359 --> 19:54.659
[ GRUNTS ]

20:01.367 --> 20:03.334
[ GRUNTS, PANTING ]

20:12.545 --> 20:14.512
HELP!

20:14.514 --> 20:17.215
SOMEBODY HELP!

20:17.917 --> 20:20.851
[ In distance ] HELP!

20:20.853 --> 20:22.920
I RAN HOME
TO GET YOU, DAD.

20:22.922 --> 20:24.722
BUT YOU WENT RUNNING
EARLY.

20:24.724 --> 20:26.591
AND BEFORE
I COULD WAKE MOM UP,

20:26.593 --> 20:29.293
YOU CAME HOME
AND YOU WERE YELLING.

20:29.295 --> 20:30.528
I WAS SO SCARED.

20:30.530 --> 20:31.829
I DIDN'T WANT TO GET
IN TROUBLE,

20:31.831 --> 20:34.665
SO I PUT MY SHOES
UNDER THE GUEST HOUSE.

20:34.667 --> 20:36.934
I'M SO SORRY.

20:36.936 --> 20:39.570
WHAT WERE YOU THINKING?

20:39.572 --> 20:41.505
NAT, IT WAS AN ACCIDENT!

20:41.507 --> 20:43.608
I SWEAR I DIDN'T MEAN TO!

20:45.745 --> 20:47.645
WHY, ABBY?

20:49.882 --> 20:50.881
WHY?!

20:52.852 --> 20:54.352
WHY DID YOU THINK

20:54.354 --> 20:56.454
THAT IF SCOTT CAME BACK
IT WOULD FIX ANYTHING?

20:56.456 --> 20:58.756
BECAUSE SHE HEARD US
FIGHTING.

20:59.859 --> 21:01.926
Ben:
WHERE AM I SUPPOSED TO GO?

21:01.928 --> 21:04.562
Christy:
GO TO YOUR GIRLFRIEND'S.

21:04.564 --> 21:06.530
SCOTT'S GONE.
YOU CAN JUST MOVE RIGHT IN.

21:06.532 --> 21:08.599
I DON'T -- I DON'T WANT TO BE
WITH JESS.

21:08.601 --> 21:10.768
IF YOU DON'T GET OUT
<i> RIGHT</i> NOW,

21:10.770 --> 21:14.772
I WILL PACK UP THE GIRLS
AND LEAVE TONIGHT!

21:14.774 --> 21:16.774
Abby: [ Crying ]
IF SCOTT CAME BACK,

21:16.776 --> 21:19.343
HE'D BE WITH JESS
AND YOU'D STAY WITH MOMMY.

21:19.345 --> 21:22.580
I JUST WANTED
TO KEEP OUR FAMILY TOGETHER.

21:22.582 --> 21:25.349
[ CRIES ]

21:27.420 --> 21:28.953
MOMMY?

21:32.492 --> 21:34.592
WHAT THE HELL
ARE WE GONNA DO?

21:34.594 --> 21:35.860
I DON'T KNOW.

21:38.398 --> 21:39.797
WE NEED TO CALL
THE POLICE.

21:39.799 --> 21:40.965
NO!

21:40.967 --> 21:42.933
NO, SHE MADE A MISTAKE.

21:42.935 --> 21:45.303
WE CAN'T LET HER
GO TO JAIL.

21:45.305 --> 21:46.737
SHE'S A BABY.

21:47.740 --> 21:49.640
WHO KILLED ONE.

21:49.642 --> 21:52.076
SHE'S YOUR SISTER.

21:52.078 --> 21:54.812
AND SHE KILLED
MY BROTHER.

21:54.814 --> 21:55.880
[ GASPS ]

21:55.882 --> 21:57.615
ABBY DIDN'T PUSH HIM

21:57.617 --> 22:00.051
OR LIE TO HIM
OR STEAL HIS STUFF.

22:00.053 --> 22:01.719
SHE KILLED HIM.

22:01.721 --> 22:03.854
I DIDN'T MEAN TO!
IT WAS AN ACCIDENT!

22:03.856 --> 22:06.824
OKAY. ALL RIGHT.
SO, TELL THE POLICE THAT.

22:06.826 --> 22:09.994
WE CAN'T KEEP THIS
A<i> SECRET.</i>

22:09.996 --> 22:12.496
IT'S POISON.
RIGHT, DAD?

22:15.868 --> 22:18.969
DON'T GO ANYWHERE.
DON'T TALK TO ANYONE.

22:18.971 --> 22:20.871
JUST WAIT FOR ME.

22:22.942 --> 22:24.542
WAIT FOR ME.

22:24.544 --> 22:27.078
WHAT --
WHAT ARE YOU GONNA DO?
FIX IT.

22:36.723 --> 22:37.888
DAD!

22:37.890 --> 22:41.425
DAD, STOP! PLEASE!

22:41.427 --> 22:42.760
DAD, PLEASE.

22:42.762 --> 22:45.062
SAY SOMETHING.

22:48.134 --> 22:50.968
WHY DID YOU PUT THAT FLASHLIGHT
BACK IN MY TRUCK?

22:50.970 --> 22:52.837
THE DETECTIVE
WAS LOOKING FOR IT,

22:52.839 --> 22:54.505
AND SHE WOULDN'T
LEAVE YOU ALONE.

22:54.507 --> 22:56.841
I KNEW IF I PUT IT BACK,
SHE'D STOP.

22:57.777 --> 22:59.944
AND THE JACKET --
HOW'D IT GET BACK TO JESS?

22:59.946 --> 23:01.545
WHEN I RAN
OUT OF THE WOODS,

23:01.547 --> 23:03.080
I REALIZED
THERE WAS BLOOD ON IT.

23:03.082 --> 23:05.649
SO, I HID IT
BEHIND MATT'S HOUSE.

23:05.651 --> 23:08.819
I DIDN'T THINK
ANYONE WOULD FIND IT.

23:08.821 --> 23:10.254
BUT THEN...

23:10.255 --> 23:11.688
YOU FOLLOWED ME
WHEN I WENT AFTER MATT

23:11.691 --> 23:12.823
AND TOOK THE JACKET.

23:12.825 --> 23:14.392
I MEAN,
I'M THE ONE WHO TOOK IT,

23:14.394 --> 23:15.960
SO I KNEW
I HAD TO GIVE IT BACK.

23:15.962 --> 23:18.462
IT WAS DIRTY,
SO I PUT IT IN THE SINK.

23:18.464 --> 23:22.733
I'M SORRY, DADDY.
I DIDN'T MEAN TO HURT TOM.

23:22.735 --> 23:25.936
THEN YOU TOLD ME
HE WAS MY BROTHER.

23:29.909 --> 23:32.943
IT WAS AN ACCIDENT.
YOU DIDN'T MEAN
TO HURT ANYONE.

23:32.945 --> 23:35.479
I WOULD TAKE IT BACK
IF I COULD.

23:35.481 --> 23:36.847
I MESSED UP.

23:43.189 --> 23:45.723
YOU'RE MINE,
AND I'M NOT GONNA LET THEM

23:45.725 --> 23:46.857
TAKE YOU FROM ME.

24:24.197 --> 24:26.764
ABBY, GO UPSTAIRS
AND PACK A BAG.

24:26.766 --> 24:27.932
WHERE ARE WE GOING?

24:27.934 --> 24:29.066
DO IT.

24:30.503 --> 24:32.670
OKAY. IT'S ALL IN THERE --
$150,000.

24:32.672 --> 24:33.838
I WANT YOU
TO TAKE THE GIRLS AND GO.

24:33.840 --> 24:35.139
Natalie:
I'M NOT GOING ANYWHERE.

24:36.476 --> 24:37.575
NAT, LISTEN TO ME.

24:37.576 --> 24:38.675
AS LONG AS
THIS CASE IS OPEN,

24:38.678 --> 24:40.044
CORNELL CAN KEEP
INVESTIGATING IT,

24:40.046 --> 24:41.111
AND SHE'S NOT GONNA STOP.

24:41.113 --> 24:42.880
YOU SAW
WHAT SHE DID TO ME.

24:42.882 --> 24:44.548
SHE'LL DO THE SAME THING
TO YOUR SISTER,

24:44.550 --> 24:45.749
ONLY WORSE
'CAUSE SHE'S A CHILD.

24:45.751 --> 24:46.884
I'M NOT GONNA
LET THAT HAPPEN.

24:46.886 --> 24:48.819
MOM, THIS IS CRAZY.

24:48.821 --> 24:50.120
I DON'T KNOW
WHAT THE RIGHT THING IS.

24:50.122 --> 24:52.022
IT SEEMS
PRETTY CLEAR TO ME.

24:52.024 --> 24:53.891
TELL THE TRUTH.
FACE IT.

24:53.893 --> 24:56.026
SHE'S 12.
SHE CAN'T FACE ANYTHING.

24:56.028 --> 24:58.629
I CAN'T BELIEVE
YOU'RE BOTH CONSIDERING THIS.

24:58.631 --> 24:59.897
EVERY DAY FOR 16 YEARS,

24:59.899 --> 25:01.932
I GOT A LECTURE
ABOUT CONSEQUENCES.

25:01.934 --> 25:02.833
WHAT HAPPENED --
NATALIE, STOP.

25:02.835 --> 25:03.968
JESS IS IN JAIL!

25:03.970 --> 25:05.603
I'LL TAKE CARE OF IT.
I'LL GET HER OUT.

25:05.605 --> 25:07.338
TOM'S DEAD, DAD.

25:07.339 --> 25:09.072
HOW ARE YOU GONNA
TAKE CARE OF<i> THAT?</i>

25:09.075 --> 25:11.008
I'M NOT GOING ANYWHERE
WITH YOU.

25:11.010 --> 25:12.977
I AM STILL YOUR MOTHER.
YOU ARE STILL A MINOR.

25:12.979 --> 25:14.111
I DON'T CARE.

25:15.214 --> 25:17.098
I WON'T GO.

25:17.099 --> 25:18.983
AND IF YOU TRY AND MAKE ME,
I WILL CALL CORNELL MYSELF.

25:18.985 --> 25:20.084
NATALIE!
NO!

25:23.956 --> 25:25.089
COME ON.

25:31.197 --> 25:32.830
WHERE DID WE
GO WRONG?

25:32.832 --> 25:33.931
I DON'T KNOW.
I DON'T KNOW.

25:33.933 --> 25:35.566
WE LOVED HER.
WE'VE TAKEN CARE OF HER.

25:35.568 --> 25:36.800
WE TAUGHT HER
RIGHT FROM WRONG.

25:36.802 --> 25:38.035
DID WE?

25:38.871 --> 25:40.237
ABBY'S GONNA NEED HELP.

25:40.238 --> 25:41.604
SHE'S GONNA HAVE TO DEAL
WITH WHAT SHE'S DONE.

25:41.607 --> 25:44.241
ARE WE DOING
THE RIGHT THING?
SHE'S OUR DAUGHTER.

25:44.243 --> 25:47.011
SHE MADE A TERRIBLE MISTAKE
THAT STARTED WITH ME,

25:47.013 --> 25:48.646
AND I GOT TO FINISH IT.

25:48.648 --> 25:49.980
HOW ARE YOU GONNA DO THAT?

25:49.982 --> 25:52.716
BY GIVING CORNELL
WHAT SHE WANTS.

25:52.718 --> 25:54.919
NOW PACK.
YOU GOT TO GO NOW.

26:01.727 --> 26:05.095
NO, JUST KEEP THAT
UP FRONT WITH YOU.

26:05.097 --> 26:07.598
WHERE'S NAT?
SHE'S NOT COMING.

26:07.600 --> 26:08.699
THEN WHAT'S GOING ON?

26:08.701 --> 26:11.001
ABBY, PLEASE.
MOM?

26:12.171 --> 26:14.838
DAD, YOU HAVE TO COME.
WE HAVE TO STAY TOGETHER.

26:14.840 --> 26:16.840
WE CAN'T RIGHT NOW.
YOU GOT TO LISTEN
TO YOUR MOTHER.

26:16.842 --> 26:18.742
I DON'T UNDERSTAND.
WHY?

26:18.744 --> 26:21.312
BECAUSE I HAVE TO STAY BEHIND
TO PROTECT YOU.

26:21.314 --> 26:22.797
HONEY.

26:22.798 --> 26:24.281
[ Voice breaking ] I'M GONNA
SEE YOU AGAIN, RIGHT?

26:25.685 --> 26:27.017
AS SOON AS I CAN.

26:28.955 --> 26:31.121
I LOVE YOU, DADDY.
IT'S GONNA BE OKAY.

26:31.123 --> 26:32.990
I PROMISE.

26:32.992 --> 26:34.992
ABBY, GET IN THE CAR.

26:35.728 --> 26:37.061
COME ON. IN THE CAR.

26:43.970 --> 26:45.269
OKAY, GO. GO.

26:48.174 --> 26:49.974
[ ENGINE TURNS OVER ]

27:02.221 --> 27:03.988
[ INHALES SHARPLY ]

27:05.925 --> 27:08.359
Natalie:
DAD, THIS IS WRONG.

27:08.361 --> 27:10.027
YOU HAVE TO SEE THAT.

27:10.029 --> 27:12.363
I MEAN,
THAT'S WHAT YOU TAUGHT ME.

27:14.900 --> 27:17.167
I HAVE TO PROTECT
YOUR SISTER.

27:18.070 --> 27:19.837
SO, WHAT ABOUT ME?

27:23.909 --> 27:25.776
DON'T I COUNT?

27:25.778 --> 27:26.944
YOU DO, SWEETHEART,

27:26.946 --> 27:29.146
IN MORE WAYS
THAN I COULD EVER TELL YOU.

27:31.350 --> 27:33.984
WHICH IS WHY IF YOU DECIDE
YOU CAN'T BE A PART OF THIS,

27:33.986 --> 27:35.052
I UNDERSTAND.

27:37.823 --> 27:40.724
BUT I'M ABBY'S FATHER,
TOO.

27:40.726 --> 27:42.926
IT WAS MY JOB
TO RAISE HER RIGHT.

27:42.928 --> 27:45.262
AND SOMEWHERE ALONG THE WAY,
I FAILED.

27:46.432 --> 27:49.733
SO, WHATEVER SHE'S DONE,
IT'S ON ME.

27:52.071 --> 27:54.405
IT'S NOT<i> YOUR</i> FAULT.

27:55.675 --> 27:57.941
Y-YOU DIDN'T FAIL ME.

28:03.416 --> 28:06.050
NAT, YOU'RE
AN AMAZING PERSON.

28:07.887 --> 28:10.954
I'M AFRAID
IT'S IN SPITE OF ME.

28:12.925 --> 28:15.325
PLEASE DON'T DO THIS.

28:53.966 --> 28:55.332
NATALIE...

28:57.002 --> 29:00.237
[ BREATHES DEEPLY ]

29:00.239 --> 29:01.839
[ BREATHES DEEPLY ]

29:01.841 --> 29:03.941
[ Sobbing ]
OH, GOD.

29:09.982 --> 29:12.416
I LOVE YOU SO MUCH.

29:12.418 --> 29:13.517
[ Crying ]
I LOVE YOU, TOO.

29:13.519 --> 29:16.086
I LOVE YOU.

29:23.496 --> 29:25.195
WHAT'S GOING ON?

29:26.866 --> 29:30.534
NAT NEEDS SOMEPLACE
TO STAY FOR A WHILE.

29:30.536 --> 29:32.903
CHRISTY WILL CALL YOU
AND EXPLAIN.

29:32.905 --> 29:35.038
WHAT ABOUT YOU, BEN?

29:36.075 --> 29:37.875
DO YOU NEED HELP?

29:39.879 --> 29:41.111
NO.

29:41.914 --> 29:43.480
BUT THANK YOU, MICHAEL.

29:51.924 --> 29:55.125
[ ENGINE TURNS OVER ]

30:14.180 --> 30:16.046
[ EXHALES SHARPLY ]

30:16.048 --> 30:18.916
NOW, ARE YOU SURE
YOU WANT TO DO THIS?

30:18.918 --> 30:22.019
I'VE MADE UP MY MIND.

30:22.021 --> 30:25.055
[ SIGHS ]

30:25.324 --> 30:27.858
THANKS FOR ALWAYS
HAVING MY BACK, MAN.

30:27.860 --> 30:30.260
[ SIGHS ]

30:30.262 --> 30:31.562
I LOVE YOU, BROTHER.

30:35.201 --> 30:36.934
I LOVE YOU, TOO.

30:45.344 --> 30:47.477
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

30:51.350 --> 30:52.416
RIGHT THIS WAY.

30:59.258 --> 31:00.641
MR. CRAWFORD?

31:00.642 --> 31:02.025
I'M HERE TO CONFESS
TO THE MURDER OF TOM MURPHY.

31:17.243 --> 31:18.942
WHAT ARE YOU
DOING HERE?

31:18.944 --> 31:21.345
DID YOU FORGET
YOU'RE REPRESENTED BY COUNSEL?

31:21.347 --> 31:23.647
WHY ARE THE COPS CALLING ME
INSTEAD OF YOU?

31:23.649 --> 31:24.615
I DON'T NEED YOU.

31:24.617 --> 31:25.916
I ALREADY TOLD THE COPS

31:25.918 --> 31:28.018
WHERE TO FIND
THE MURDER WEAPON.

31:28.020 --> 31:29.586
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

31:29.588 --> 31:32.089
I'M CONFESSING.

31:32.091 --> 31:33.657
I KILLED TOM.

31:34.627 --> 31:37.060
I DON'T BELIEVE YOU.

31:37.062 --> 31:38.629
THAT'S NOT MY PROBLEM.

31:38.631 --> 31:40.364
I SAT HERE FOR HOURS

31:40.365 --> 31:42.098
WHILE YOU TOLD US
WHAT HAPPENED THAT NIGHT.

31:42.101 --> 31:44.301
I LIED.

31:44.303 --> 31:47.938
I CAN'T
LET YOU DO THIS, BEN.

31:48.908 --> 31:50.908
YOU DON'T HAVE TO, JOE.

31:50.910 --> 31:52.109
YOU'RE FIRED.

31:57.049 --> 31:58.649
YOU'RE A FOOL.

32:07.927 --> 32:10.060
I'LL BE REPRESENTING
MYSELF.

32:10.062 --> 32:13.063
CAN WE GET STARTED?

32:13.065 --> 32:14.932
YOU DO REALIZE,
MR. CRAWFORD,

32:14.934 --> 32:18.068
YOU'VE ALREADY BEEN CLEARED
AS A SUSPECT IN TOM'S MURDER.

32:20.239 --> 32:22.039
YOU WERE WRONG.

32:31.317 --> 32:34.151
WHENEVER YOU'RE READY.

32:34.153 --> 32:38.488
<i> IT'S JANUARY 2, 2015,</i>
<i> 12:30 P.M.</i>

32:38.490 --> 32:42.025
PRESENT ARE
ANDREA CORNELL, HOMICIDE,

32:42.027 --> 32:43.493
AND BEN CRAWFORD.

32:45.230 --> 32:47.431
I LIED TO YOU.

32:47.433 --> 32:50.100
I DID KNOW TOM WAS MY SON.

32:52.504 --> 32:55.038
ONCE I TOLD CHRISTY
THAT I SLEPT WITH JESS,

32:55.040 --> 32:57.007
I KNEW IT WAS ONLY
A MATTER OF TIME

32:57.009 --> 32:58.508
BEFORE SHE REALIZED
THE TRUTH

32:58.510 --> 33:00.077
AND I WOULD LOSE MY FAMILY.

33:02.314 --> 33:04.481
SO, I KNEW
WHAT I HAD TO DO.

33:05.985 --> 33:10.187
I USED NAT'S KEY,
LET MYSELF IN.

33:10.189 --> 33:11.221
TOM TRUSTED ME.

33:11.223 --> 33:14.124
HE WOULD HAVE
FOLLOWED ME ANYWHERE.

33:15.060 --> 33:18.261
I TOOK HIM
INTO THE WOODS,

33:18.263 --> 33:20.430
AND I KILLED HIM.

33:25.371 --> 33:27.437
THEN I WENT HOME,

33:27.439 --> 33:29.272
CLEANED MYSELF UP,

33:29.274 --> 33:32.342
AND WENT OUT
FOR AN EARLY RUN

33:32.344 --> 33:35.112
SO I COULD BE THE ONE
TO DISCOVER HIS BODY.

33:47.693 --> 33:50.761
WERE YOU
VERY ANGRY WITH TOM?

33:50.763 --> 33:52.662
NO.

33:52.664 --> 33:56.166
I JUST DIDN'T WANT CHRISTY
TO FIND HIM.

33:56.168 --> 34:00.070
THEN SIX BLOWS TO THE HEAD
SEEMS A LITTLE EXCESSIVE,

34:00.072 --> 34:01.738
DON'T YOU THINK?

34:10.315 --> 34:13.683
I DON'T KNOW
HOW MANY TIMES I...HIT HIM.

34:13.685 --> 34:15.452
I WAS DRUGGED.

34:19.691 --> 34:21.158
[ KNOCK ON WINDOW ]

34:28.367 --> 34:30.634
[ DOOR OPENS, CLOSES ]

34:34.773 --> 34:36.840
CAN YOU GIVE US A SECOND,
PLEASE?
Man: YES, SIR.

34:39.812 --> 34:41.078
I GOT IT.

34:43.482 --> 34:44.681
WHAT ARE YOU DOING,
DETECTIVE?

34:44.683 --> 34:46.416
I'M LISTENING TO
A FALSE CONFESSION.

34:46.418 --> 34:48.552
WHAT I HEARD WAS YOU
ABOUT TO TANK MY CASE.

34:48.554 --> 34:50.287
HE'S LYING
TO PROTECT HIS DAUGHTER.

34:50.289 --> 34:52.373
OH, CAN YOU PROVE THAT?

34:52.374 --> 34:54.458
ABBY OVERHEARD HER PARENTS
ARGUING ABOUT JESS MURPHY.

34:54.460 --> 34:55.859
SHE WAS MAD AND JEALOUS.

34:55.861 --> 34:58.195
TOM WAS THE SON
THAT BEN ALWAYS WANTED.

34:58.197 --> 35:00.797
ARE YOU FINISHED?
BLOOD SPATTER SHOWED
THAT THE VICTIM

35:00.799 --> 35:03.133
WAS STRUCK BY SOMEONE
NO TALLER THAN 5 FEET.

35:03.135 --> 35:04.267
ABBY CRAWFORD.

35:04.269 --> 35:05.769
AND WHEN I PUT
AN EXPERT ON THE STAND

35:05.771 --> 35:06.803
TO TESTIFY TO THAT,

35:06.805 --> 35:08.438
THE DEFENSE
IS GONNA SHUT ME DOWN

35:08.440 --> 35:09.773
BECAUSE OUR LAB
WAS COMPROMISED.

35:09.775 --> 35:11.775
ABBY WAS ON A BUS
THAT DROPPED HER OFF

35:11.777 --> 35:13.376
AT THE ENTRANCE
OF THE CUL-DE-SAC

35:13.378 --> 35:14.778
RIGHT BEFORE
THE BLUE JACKET

35:14.780 --> 35:16.413
REAPPEARED
AT JESS MURPHY'S HOUSE.

35:16.415 --> 35:20.150
SHE PLANTED THE EVIDENCE
TO FRAME THE BOY'S MOTHER.

35:20.819 --> 35:22.752
A LITTLE GIRL ON A BUS?

35:22.754 --> 35:24.855
MOM TOOK THE KIDS
AND SHE LEFT.

35:24.857 --> 35:27.124
ABBY MISSED HER DAD.
END OF STORY.

35:27.126 --> 35:28.792
YOU GOT THE WRONG GUY.

35:28.793 --> 35:30.459
I ASKED YOU FOR A CONFESSION
AND A MURDER WEAPON.

35:30.462 --> 35:32.362
CRIME TECHS JUST BROUGHT ME
THE FLASHLIGHT,

35:32.364 --> 35:33.597
SO NOW I HAVE BOTH.

35:33.598 --> 35:34.831
CRAWFORD'S GETTING
25 YEARS TO LIFE.

35:34.833 --> 35:36.366
THAT'S A WIN
ANY DAY OF THE WEEK.

35:36.368 --> 35:38.768
HE DID NOT KILL TOM.

35:38.770 --> 35:39.903
THIS CASE IS CLOSED.

35:39.905 --> 35:41.671
AND IF YOU KEEP
INVESTIGATING,

35:41.673 --> 35:43.373
YOU'RE GONNA
LOSE YOUR BADGE.

35:43.375 --> 35:46.376
PUT THE WRONG GUY AWAY,
YOU CAN HAVE MY BADGE.

36:02.127 --> 36:04.761
[ BUZZER ]
Man: RIGHT. YEAH.

36:12.838 --> 36:14.471
CAN YOU GIVE US
A MINUTE?

36:16.241 --> 36:18.308
YOU GOT IT.

36:18.310 --> 36:19.709
YOU'RE MAKING
A MISTAKE.

36:19.711 --> 36:22.746
[ BUZZER ]
I CONFESSED.
IT'S OVER.

36:22.748 --> 36:25.315
YOU'RE NOT
PROTECTING ABBY.

36:25.317 --> 36:27.918
SHE HAD THIS PLANNED
FOR SOME TIME.

36:27.920 --> 36:30.887
SHE DIDN'T JUST ATTACK TOM
OUT OF AN IMPULSE

36:30.889 --> 36:33.323
BECAUSE SHE OVERHEARD
YOU AND YOUR WIFE ARGUE.

36:33.325 --> 36:34.958
YOU DON'T KNOW
WHAT YOU'RE TALKING ABOUT.

36:34.960 --> 36:38.495
IT WAS PREMEDITATED MURDER.
SHE LURED HIM.

36:38.497 --> 36:40.197
SHE TOOK HIM
DOWN TO THE RIVER,

36:40.199 --> 36:41.331
AND WHEN HE PANICKED,

36:41.333 --> 36:43.200
SHE HIT HIM ON THE HEAD
REPEATEDLY.

36:43.202 --> 36:45.302
THAT WAS RAGE,

36:45.303 --> 36:47.403
AND IT WAS A RAGE
I WITNESSED AT THE FIREWORKS.

36:48.207 --> 36:49.406
YOU<i> WERE</i> THERE.

36:50.275 --> 36:51.841
I CHASE KILLERS.

36:51.843 --> 36:54.878
SHE DIDN'T ACCIDENTALLY
DROP HER PHONE.

36:54.880 --> 36:57.647
SHE SAW THE AFFECTION
BETWEEN YOU AND JESS,

36:57.649 --> 37:01.351
AND THEN SHE SMASHED HER PHONE
TO THE GROUND.

37:01.353 --> 37:03.220
Abby: AAH!

37:03.222 --> 37:06.590
ABBY IS CALLOUS,
SHE'S UNEMOTIONAL,
SHE'S VIOLENT.

37:06.592 --> 37:09.793
SHE INJECTED HERSELF
INTO THIS INVESTIGATION

37:09.795 --> 37:10.860
AGAIN AND AGAIN.

37:10.862 --> 37:12.729
DO YOU KNOW
WHAT HAPPENED?

37:16.768 --> 37:19.936
ABBY'S A CHILD.
SHE HAD NOTHING
TO DO WITH THIS.

37:19.938 --> 37:24.307
BEN, NO MATTER
WHAT YOU THINK,

37:24.309 --> 37:28.845
PUTTING MY DAUGHTER AWAY
INTO PRISON

37:28.847 --> 37:31.815
WAS THE HARDEST THING
I EVER HAD TO DO.

37:31.817 --> 37:35.485
THIS WASN'T AN ACCIDENT.
IT WASN'T A MISTAKE.

37:35.487 --> 37:37.921
ABBY BRUTALLY KILLED
YOUR SON.

37:37.923 --> 37:40.790
AND IF YOU LET HER
GET AWAY WITH THAT,

37:40.792 --> 37:44.361
TOM WILL NOT BE
HER LAST VICTIM.

37:46.865 --> 37:48.765
IT WAS MY FAULT.

37:49.801 --> 37:51.401
I KILLED TOM.

37:52.804 --> 37:54.871
[ CHAINS JINGLING ]

38:01.913 --> 38:03.446
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

38:04.549 --> 38:07.584
