40:09.441 --> 40:10.673
Barrett: HELLO.

40:12.477 --> 40:13.943
HOW DID YOU HEAR?

40:13.945 --> 40:15.979
I WAS DOING A CONSULT
AT THE, UH, JAIL

40:15.981 --> 40:18.181
WHEN BEN CRAWFORD
WAS BEING PROCESSED.

40:18.183 --> 40:20.817
OH, SO, YOU'VE COME
TO PICK UP THE PIECES?

40:20.819 --> 40:24.888
I KNOW
YOU HATE TO LOSE.

40:24.890 --> 40:28.858
DIVORCE MEANS NEVER HAVING TO
EXPLAIN YOURSELF.

40:28.860 --> 40:30.660
I'M JUST HERE
TO LISTEN.

40:30.662 --> 40:33.463
OR TO TALK YOU OFF A LEDGE
OR WHATEVER YOU NEED.

40:33.465 --> 40:36.533
LET'S JUST DO
A POST MORTEM.

40:36.535 --> 40:38.067
FATHER PROTECTS DAUGHTER

40:38.069 --> 40:41.204
WHO UNINTENTIONALLY
COMMITS A CRIME.
NO.

40:41.206 --> 40:43.940
THAT'S WHAT YOU TRIED TO DO
WITH JENNIFER.

40:43.942 --> 40:46.709
IT'S DELUDED MAN
COVERS FOR PSYCHOPATH.

40:46.711 --> 40:48.361
SHE'S 12.

40:48.362 --> 40:50.012
KILLERS ARE GETTING YOUNGER
EVERY YEAR.

40:50.015 --> 40:51.748
HE THINKS
HE'S HELPING HER.

40:51.750 --> 40:52.782
THERE'S NO TREATMENT.

40:52.784 --> 40:53.983
HER BRAIN
IS STILL DEVELOPING --

40:53.985 --> 40:56.619
INTO A BETTER KILLER.

40:56.621 --> 40:58.021
[ SCOFFS ]

40:59.024 --> 41:01.157
THERE'S NOTHING
YOU CAN DO ABOUT IT.

41:02.794 --> 41:03.893
YES, THERE IS.

41:03.895 --> 41:05.728
ALL RIGHT.

41:06.798 --> 41:08.665
LET'S GO.

41:09.568 --> 41:12.702
I'M GONNA PUT
ABBY CRAWFORD AWAY.

41:31.490 --> 41:33.790
EVERYTHING'S GONNA BE OKAY,
ABBY.

41:37.896 --> 41:39.796
WHEN'S DADDY COMING?

41:42.934 --> 41:44.567
I DON'T KNOW.

41:46.104 --> 41:48.271
I WAS SURE JESS
WOULD MOVE AWAY.

41:50.642 --> 41:51.708
WHAT?

41:55.847 --> 41:57.881
NONE OF THIS
WOULD HAVE HAPPENED

41:57.883 --> 42:00.016
IF I JUST GOT TOM
TO THE RIVER.
